---
import FaultyTerminal from './FaultyTerminal.astro';
---

<section id="thesis" class="bg-white dark:bg-accent-800 py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-primary-500 mb-4">Investment Thesis</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-secondary-500 dark:text-white">
        Deep software. Lean businesses.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-300">
        We invest in founders who know their industry inside out and need a technical partner to bring their vision to market. The products we build together are packed with hard-won domain knowledge and solved edge cases that aren't easily replicated. We use AI to accelerate how they're built and to run lean, automated businesses around them.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-px bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:ring-gray-700">
      <div class="relative bg-accent-700 dark:bg-accent-600 lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-2 overflow-hidden">
        <FaultyTerminal tint="#fccd59" scale={1.5} brightness={0.2} />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-accent-700/95 via-accent-700/60 to-transparent dark:from-accent-600/95 dark:via-accent-600/60 dark:to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 p-8 lg:p-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-primary-400">Core Thesis</p>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-400/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">AI-Native Businesses</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Our portfolio companies are built on deep domain knowledge and hard-won edge cases that can't be replicated overnight. We use AI to accelerate how these products are built and to run lean, automated businesses around them.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-accent-800 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-400/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary-500 dark:text-white">Domain Experts</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Non-technical founders with deep vertical knowledge and an existing network of potential customers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-accent-800 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-400/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary-500 dark:text-white">High ACV B2B</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Enterprise and mid-market SaaS with high average contract values. Fewer customers needed to reach profitability.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-accent-800 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-400/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.066 2.573c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573 1.066c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066-2.573c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary-500 dark:text-white">Hands-On Partnership</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Founders who want a technical co-founder, not a passive investor. We take stakes through joint ventures, founding equity, and sweat equity &mdash; and we build the product alongside you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
